	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 10th level, you gain the following features:</p><ul><li><p>Your prestige rating is increased by an amount equal to your Proficiency Bonus.</p></li><li><p>When you roll initiative, if you have no remaining @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.SdkTtahNdnXE8OEA]{Legend Dice}, you regain 1 Legend Die.</p></li><li><p>Additionally, when you expend a Legend Die to enhance a combat maneuver, you may choose to reroll the maneuver’s damage but you must take the new result.</p></li></ul>",
